    <svcsubproc>
        <title>D.O.T. Lights and Reflectors</title>
        <para>D.O.T. marker lights and reflectors are located in various positions around the body.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove lens on marker light to access bulb for replacement.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen and remove lens mounting screw in center of lens assembly.</para>
            <figure id="f47003107" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g47003107.webp" filename="../figg47/G47003107.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1"
                         scalefitwidth="232px" scalefitheight="232px"/>
                <caption>Figure 107. D.O.T. Light Removal</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">LENS AND LIGHT MOUNTING SCREW</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Replace bulb as necessary.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Reflectors are replaceable by removing the center screw.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
